    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Bonus: Indica vs Sativa (Quick Reality Check)</h2>
      <p>Most shelf strains are hybrids. Effects are shaped by <strong>terpenes + dose + your body</strong>. Use the label as a starting point and take notes to find your sweet spot.</p>
      <a class="cta" href="https://www.ilovegrowingmarijuana.com/growing/germinating-autoflower-seeds/?aff=7946" rel="sponsored noopener" target="_blank">Beginner Germination Guide →</a>
