  <section class="faq">
    <h2>FAQs</h2>
    <details><summary>Do autos need total darkness?</summary><p>No. They aren’t triggered by dark period length. Focus on airflow, temp, and RH; 18/6 or 20/4 schedules work well.</p></details>
    <details><summary>What’s a safe first edible dose if I grow edibles later?</summary><p>2–5 mg THC, or 1–2 mg THC with 5–10 mg CBD. Wait 2 hours before redosing.</p></details>
    <details><summary>How do I avoid overwatering?</summary><p>Let pots get lighter, water in a ring, and ensure an airy mix with extra perlite.</p></details>
  </section>

